{"tid":373534,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(Steam)100%香港本土製作遊戲","createTime":"2017-08-25T05:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T06:35:39.000Z","uid":140116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfefef5e9f1c15b1139be091709cc9990490ccb9","tid":373534,"uid":140116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:33:29.000Z","msg":"　　各位巴打大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n　　最近小弟同友人合作整左隻視覺小說，產品名叫《SOULS》，放埋上去Steam賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n　　希望各位多多支持，埋黎睇下啦～<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝以下係產品介紹＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201706/e1481716447cdcc41e26cb0bc1a8b30e.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201706%2Fe1481716447cdcc41e26cb0bc1a8b30e.PNG&h=af9cc417&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n　　Steam商店頁面：<a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/677790/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F677790%2F&d=YkKN8ErseoKdUdwvRorTiNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=6f37c507\" target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/677790/</a><br />\n　　遊戲名稱：SOULS<br />\n　　製作團隊：Team Fork<br />\n　　類型：視覺小說 (Visual Novel)（*單線型故事。）<br />\n　　語言：繁體中文, English<br />\n　　發售平台：Steam<br />\n　　發售日期：現已發售<br />\n　　<span style=\"color: navy;\">售價：港幣 $59</span><br />\n　　故事簡介：時值秋季，校園裡不知何起開始流傳著一個傳聞－－某個荒廢的水塘裡有一隻名叫人蛇的怪物。主角（男孩）為了查明真相，便前往水塘探險，結果居然遇見傳聞中的怪物，從此陰差陽錯地與牠建構出一段既非朋友、既非家人、既非飼主與寵物的奇妙關係。到底人蛇的真身是什麼呢？牠又會為男孩帶來什麼影響呢？隨著劇情推進，校園裡不停發生難以解釋的怪事，連串謎題和事件似乎都與這一人一怪的組合有千絲萬縷的關係，到底真相為何？故事由此展開&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝介紹完畢＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n　　有乜問題同意見歡迎各位留言討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a7afac310e0f0d303d261f3862abf6a2642e66","tid":373534,"uid":36050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:36:53.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"a1067e3c44e